title: About Me
content: Hello, my name is Khaled Djeriou and I am a Flutter web developer. I specialize in developing beautiful and responsive web applications using Flutter. I am passionate about creating user-friendly and intuitive interfaces that provide a seamless user experience. I have experience working with various clients and I am always eager to take on new challenges. Please feel free to contact me at khaled.djeriou@gmail.com for any inquiries or project proposals .
